translation.user_onboarding_welcome_description: MSQ platform allows you to invest in crypto tokens and other financial instruments. Let's take a tour of the dashboard page to help you navigate it with ease.
translation.user_onboarding_description_dashboard: Explore your investment portfolio, track token transactions, and manage your financial instruments in one place.
translation.user_onboarding_description_platforms: Manage and review all your investment platforms in one location, track their performance, and update their operational statuses.
translation.user_onboarding_description_platform_req: Review and manage incoming requests for platform additions or modifications conveniently in one place.
translation.user_onboarding_description_tokens: Browse, manage, and track detailed information on all your tokens, including balance, status, and chain details.
translation.user_onboarding_description_users: Access comprehensive details and manage all user profiles, including individual and corporate accounts, to ensure optimal platform engagement.
translation.user_onboarding_description_news: Create and manage news posts that keep your users informed about the latest updates and important announcements.
translation.user_onboarding_description_popups: Design and oversee promotional popups that engage your audience with timely offers and announcements.
translation.user_onboarding_description_notification: Create and dispatch timely notifications to engage your audience with the latest information and alerts.
translation.user_onboarding_description_ads_manageme: Efficiently manage your advertising campaigns by editing, deleting, and reviewing images and details for each ad.
translation.user_onboarding_description_inquiry: Manage and respond to user inquiries efficiently, ensuring a direct line of communication for resolving issues and answering questions.
translation.user_onboarding_description_P2U_manageme: Oversee the RPA history of all members, monitor RPA error logs, and adjust the accumulation settings for P2U points to optimize operational efficiency.
translation.user_onboarding_description_super_save: Manage financial transactions, view reports, access vault details, and utilize support services, along with tracking admin activities and educational resources on Super Save.
translation.user_onboarding_description_admin_users: Manage your platform's administrative users efficiently, overseeing permissions, and taking actions like approval or disapproval for admin status.
translation.user_onboarding_description_change_time_: Adjust your platform's time zone setting to align with your local time for synchronized operations.
translation.user_onboarding_description_change_langu: Switch between English and Korean to navigate the platform in your preferred language.
translation.user_onboarding_description_profile: Access your account settings and log out options from this menu.
